Introduction

About vibrational marketing

We are strong believers that living & working in alignment provides the most positively abundant outcome.

At Creatiq out point of difference is something known as Vibrational Marketing. We work with business owners to align their vision and life's mission with their business objective to reach the heart of their audience.

When alginment occurs, higher vibrational (resonance) takes place ushering the way for pure abundance.
